OL,3,CMan who 'inspired millions' with
OL,4,Ccandid cancer reflections dies
OL,6,FAnother colleague, Ed Lewis, says: "It
OL,7,Ftakes so much courage and bravery to
OL,8,Fwrite about such a difficult subject
OL,9,Fand he made it so much more
OL,10,Fapproachable amd accessible and
OL,11,Fthat'll be his legacy."
OL,13,FSimon was a volunteer for several
OL,14,Fother groups including the Samaritans.
OL,16,FHis selfless nature was exemplified
OL,17,Fthrough a series of candid articles
OL,18,Fthat he wrote for a local newspaper
OL,19,Ffollowing his terminal diagnosis,
OL,20,Fdetailing his treatment and
OL,21,Freflections.
