OL,3,CMan who 'inspired millions' with
OL,4,Ccandid cancer reflections dies
OL,6,FThe pieces went viral and were read
OL,7,Fworldwide with many taking comfort
OL,8,Ffrom his words as they faced their own
OL,9,Fcancer journeys.
OL,11,FSimon's tireless work to make other
OL,12,Fpeople's lives better was recognised
OL,13,Fas he was awarded the rare Silver Seal
OL,14,Fby Jersey Bailiff, Sir Timothy Le Cocq.
OL,16,FShortly before his death, Simon
OL,17,Freceived a personal letter from King
OL,18,FCharles III who praised his
OL,19,F"courageous approach" to his cancer
OL,20,Fdiagnosis and his charitable service.
